---
title: Pea and Pancetta Penne with Parmesan, Pine Nuts, and Mint
description: Just a small amount of pancetta imparts bold flavor into any recipe. We love the combination of salty pancetta, sweet peas, and sharp parmesan cheese. This creamy pasta is guaranteed to please even the pickiest of eaters.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d5c3d94dab71ce7e8b4567.jpg
